name: Verify Infab Kartor Is Visible and Returns HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
fullName: Test Suites.Health Check External Resources.Verify Infab Kartor Is Visible and Returns HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
description:
Test steps:
1. Navigate to kartor och zoner
2. Verify URL
3. Expand kartor och zoner
4. Click on kartor och zoner interaktiv karta
5. Verify URL
6. Verify HTTP status code is 200
